query:
SELECT s.id, s.studentId, s.workoutId, s.workoutDayIndex, s.status, s.scheduledAt, w.name as workoutName
FROM sessions s
LEFT JOIN workouts w ON s.workoutId = w.id
WHERE s.deletedAt IS NULL
ORDER BY s.scheduledAt DESC
LIMIT 20;
